{"tid":174253,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"城邦皇室秘密聚會：為香港建立海外根據地尋址覓地","createTime":"2017-03-26T16:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T16:03:36.000Z","uid":47194,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40a54ae1be125a87aa5fd363a71c27332e12c3ef","tid":174253,"uid":47194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T16:01:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/03/26/155854/%E5%9F%8E%E9%82%A6%E7%9A%87%E5%AE%A4%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E8%81%9A%E6%9C%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2017%2F03%2F26%2F155854%2F%25E5%259F%258E%25E9%2582%25A6%25E7%259A%2587%25E5%25AE%25A4%25E7%25A7%2598%25E5%25AF%2586%25E8%2581%259A%25E6%259C%2583%2F&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRziwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=4224c9f1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/03/26/155854/%E5%9F%8E%E9%82%A6%E7%9A%87%E5%AE%A4%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E8%81%9A%E6%9C%83/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/26/155854/%E5%9F%8E%E9%82%A6%E7%9A%87%E5%AE%A4%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E8%81%9A%E6%9C%83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F26%2F155854%2F%25E5%259F%258E%25E9%2582%25A6%25E7%259A%2587%25E5%25AE%25A4%25E7%25A7%2598%25E5%25AF%2586%25E8%2581%259A%25E6%259C%2583.jpg&h=8a07f075&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說林鄭以777票高票當選特首，香港再次進入「最黑暗的一天」，網上社運人士一片哀嚎之際，一向眾人皆醉我獨醒嘅城邦派反而雄心壯志，紛紛為新計劃盤算。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n事緣國師陳雲尋日就出Post，話打算唔玩城邦論，改而在海外建立香港根據地，正當編輯部一眾紐倫堡之友食住花生睇爛尾，結果城邦派軍曹網友反應熱烈，為呢個二十一世紀驚天地泣鬼神嘅皇天上帝挪亞方舟計劃出謀獻策。"},{"pid":"ce2c317dabf0a62441528fb9e4d4f6b664ab231d","tid":174253,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T16:03:36.000Z","msg":"去海外買樓？"}]}